title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show NOV-01-2013 FRI
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show NOV-01-2013 FRI    PODCAST







Dennis Prager Radio Show



Prager 20131101  3 Open Lines

Prager H3: Per usual, callers set the agenda.
 Issues raised include: 
 Because Dennis was always tall was he expected to play basketball in high school;
 how bad is ObamaCare, really;
 how do you honor a parent who is an unrepentant drunk.




Prager 20131101  2 Happiness Hour: Pre Existing Philosophy

Prager H2: You need a world view or a philosophy in advance of tragedy and pain.





Prager 20131101  1 Brown Shirts

Prager H1: At from Brown University earlier this week NY City Police Chief,
 Ray Kelly, was shouted off the stage and his planned speech cancelled.
 This travesty is emblematic of so much that is wrong with higher education.
 Statements by students and some administrators are priceless and sick-making.
